Get-Process | Sort WS -Descending | Select -First 10	
    - Finds the top memory-consuming processes.

Get-ChildItem C:\ -Directory ... Measure 
    - Length	Calculates the largest folders on a drive.

Get-CimInstance Win32_LogicalDisk | Where {$_.FreeSpace/1GB -lt 10}	
    - Finds drives with less than 10 GB free.

Restart-Service Spooler	
    - Restarts the Print Spooler to resolve printing issues.

Get-CimInstance Win32_StartupCommand	
    - Lists programs that launch automatically at startup.
